data.description: Incredible unique Mid Century Modern, brick, ranch home that offers nothing but endless potential and timelessness on a corner lot! Spacious 1460 sqft interior with 3 bedrooms, 2 bath, one level living or extend into the full basement! Private fenced in back yard, and beautiful landscaping in the front. Original hardwoods and details throughout the home! 1 car attached garage plus additional 20 x 32 detached garage for additional storage outside! Don't miss your chance to own this one of a kind property!
